<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Shawartaccen Tsarin Taron Addu'a</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Addu'ar buɗe taron addu'a
 2) Waƙoƙin yabo (1 ko 2)
 3) Shaidar godiya baki-baki
 4) Addu'ar godiya
 5) Waƙoƙin ɗaukakar Allah
 6) Damar faɗin roƙe-roke, bukatu, abin addu'a baki-baki
 7) Addu'ar tare domin Lamba 6: baki-baki ko gabaɗaya
 8) Waƙoƙin yabo
 9) Addu'ar rufe taro</lyrics>
</song>